quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  3,30,"Г‘alnde Darngal, woЕ‹kii kala taway golle makki kin immorde e moЖґЖґere; Й—um no Й“annaa Й—uytaaka, e kon ko ki golli immorde e bone; hiki yoloo sinno wonayno hakkunde makki e majje dummunne woЙ—Й—uЙ—o. Hol no heЙ“irta on yela?! Alla No ReЕ‹tina on e Hoore Mun, wata faggito bakkaatu ko O Tikkirana on. Alla ko HilnotooЙ—o jeyaaЙ“e Й“en; ko Й—um waЙ—i si Mo ReЕ‹tina Й“e HulЙ“ina Й“e."
  3,31,"Maaku an NulaaЙ—o: "Si on laatike ko on yiЙ—uЙ“e Alla haqqan, jokkee kon ko mi addi; ko feeГ±i e ko wirnii e mun, daГ±on Giggol Alla, O Haforana on junubaaji mon". Alla ko Haforanoowo kala on tuubuЙ—o e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, YurmeteeЙ—o Й“e."
  3,32,"Maaku an NulaaЙ—o: "ЖЉoftoree Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, Г±emtinorgol yamirooje Й—en woЙ—Й—itoo haЙ—aaЙ—i Й—in", si Й“e Й—uurnike Й—um, pellet, Allah yiЙ—aa heeferЙ“e lunndotooЙ“e yamirooje Makko Й—en kaЕ‹ko e NulaaЙ—o Makko on."
  3,33,"Pellet, Alla SuЙ“ike Aadama (yo o his), O Yamiri Malaa'ika en Makko Й“e sujjani mo, O SuЙ“ii kadi Nuuhu, O WaЙ—i mo adaaЙ—o Nuleede e yimЙ“e leydi ndin, O SuЙ“ii kadi yimЙ“e Ibraahiima Й“en, O WaЙ—i Annabaaku ngun heddiingu e jurriiya maЙ“Й“e, O SuЙ“ii kadi yimЙ“e Imraana Й“en; O SuЙ“ori Й“ee Й—oo kala O ЖЃurni Й“e e yimЙ“e jamaanu maЙ“Й“e."
  3,34,"ЖЃee AnnabaaЙ“e e jurriyaaji mun jaЕ‹taaЙ“e dow Й—oo, jokkunooЙ“e laawol mun, ko Й“e jurriiya yoga e maЙ“Й“e iwde e yoga; ka bajjinЙ—ingol Alla huuwa moЖґЖґuЙ—i, hiЙ“e ronindira teddule e Й“ure. Alla ko Nanoowa jeewte jeyaaЙ“e Makko, AnnduЙ—o kuuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e; ko Й—um O SuЙ“oraЕ‹ta on mo O Muuyi e maЙ“Й“e."
  3,35,"JaЕ‹to an Annbiijo, tuma nde debbo Imraana on yumma Maryama (yo Й“e his) wi'unoo: "Joomi an, min mi waЙ—Й—inanii hoore-am nde mi waЙ—aЕ‹ta koo ko mi sowii ka reedu am fii heertinanaaЙ—um fii MaaЙ—a, rinЙ—inaaЙ—um e kala huunde; fii no Й—um kurkorano Maa kurkanoo Suudu Maa ndun, JaЙ“anam Й—um, pellet, An ko A Nanoowo toraare am, AnnduЙ—o annuyee am"."
  3,36,"Nde o jibinnoo boobo on, o wi'i himo ngaЕ‹tinoo -tawde o yelinoke nde boobo on laatotoo gorel: "Joomi an, min mi jibinii mo deyel". Ko Alla Й“uri Anndude ko o jibini kon, gorko mo o joortinoo on laataaki wano debbo mo o yeЙ—aa on; ka doole e ka tagudi. "Min non, mi innii mo Maryama, min mi moolnorii Ma mo kaЕ‹ko e jurriiya makko on, immorde e seytaane raЙ—aaЙ—o e Yurmeende Maa"."
  3,37,"Alla JaЙ“irani mo takke makko Й—en jaЙ“annde moЖґЖґunde, O Ne'iri mo needi moЖґЖґundi, O WaЙ—i e makko Й“ernde moЖґЖґuЙ“e Й“en e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, O Halfini mo Jakairaa'u (yo o his). Tuma kala nde Jakariyaa'u tawunoo mo ka rewirde, o tawdayno mo e arsike laaЙ“uЙ—o newiiЙ—o, O lamdoo oo debbo: "Hey Maryam, ko hoЕ‹to oo arsike maa iwri?". O jaaboo mo: "Oo arsike ko ka Alla iwri", pellet, Alla no Arsika on mo O Muuyi; arsike yaajuЙ—o, ko aldaa e hasboore."